cs.AR, cs.ET, cs.SY, cs.EM, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the integration of a deep learning accelerator into a RISC-V SoC and evaluates its performance using a specific algorithm. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), cs.ET (Embedded Systems), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.EM (Emerging Technologies), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
